		"name": "Revamp",
		"description": "## **1\\. Registration & Verification**\n\n1. **Register User**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"username\": \"...\", \"email\": \"...\", \"password\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Expect: Success, welcome email with OTP sent.\n        \n2. **Verify User OTP**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/verify-otp`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"email\": \"...\", \"otp\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Use the OTP from the welcome email.\n        \n    - Expect: Success, user is now verified.\n        \n3. **Resend Verification OTP** (optional)\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/resend-otp`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"email\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Expect: New OTP sent to email.\n        \n\n---\n\n## **2\\. Authentication**\n\n1. **Login**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/login`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"email\": \"...\", \"password\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Expect: Success, JWT cookie set.\n        \n2. **Logout**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/logout`\n        \n    - (Requires authentication/JWT cookie)\n        \n    - Expect: Success, JWT cookie cleared.\n        \n\n---\n\n## **3\\. Password Management**\n\n1. **Forgot Password**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/forgot-password`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"email\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Expect: OTP sent to email.\n        \n2. **Reset Password**\n    \n    - `POST /api/users/reset-password`\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"email\": \"...\", \"otp\": \"...\", \"newPassword\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Use OTP from previous step.\n        \n    - Expect: Success, password updated.\n        \n\n---\n\n## **4\\. Profile Management**\n\n1. **Get Current User Profile**\n    \n    - `GET /api/users/me`\n        \n    - (Requires authentication/JWT cookie)\n        \n    - Expect: User profile data.\n        \n2. **Update Profile (including password and avatar)**\n    \n    - `PATCH /api/users/me`\n        \n    - (Requires authentication/JWT cookie)\n        \n    - Body: `{ \"username\": \"...\", \"email\": \"...\", \"currentPassword\": \"...\", \"newPassword\": \"...\" }`\n        \n    - Or use form-data for avatar upload.\n        \n    - Expect: Profile updated.\n        \n\n---\n\n## **5\\. Admin/Extended (if needed for your role)**\n\n1. **Get All Users**\n    \n    - `GET /api/users`\n        \n    - (If protected, use admin credentials)\n        \n2. **Get User by ID**\n    \n    - `GET /api/users/:id`\n        \n3. **Update User by ID**\n    \n    - `PATCH /api/users/:id`\n        \n4. **Delete User**\n    \n    - `DELETE /api/users/:id`",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "29987377"
	},
